    "Finally, just present a brief comment from the perspective of application.",
    "Any form of discretization of an originally continuous space will inevitably bring about symmetry breaking.",
    "In numerical simulation, symmetry breakings from different dimensions are coupled together to make effects.",
    "In the study of specific discrete format, not only the numerical accuracy but also the numerical stability should be guaranteed.",
